I decided to do one featuring two RA characters.

For lulz.

So here\'s Renaza from the first frame:
Where do you go to actually view the comic? You keep showing us all these images but give us no links... I call shenanigans!

Where do you go to actually view the comic? You keep showing us all these images but give us no links... I call shenanigans!

Considering the images so far all appear to be preliminary work, it would be sensible to assume that the comic doesn\'t actually exist yet.

HOTE- lolno

But honestly, your art is certainly getting better. Good job man. (not saying it was bad before, it was still great)

Yes, most of it is preliminary, and most of it is buffer that is going to be re-done anyway.

Here\'s my site: www.rankamateur.thecomicseries.com
